# Release Notes BPMN-Studio v5.4.0

This changelog _only_ covers the changes between [v5.3.0 and v5.4.0](https://github.com/process-engine/bpmn-studio/compare/v5.3.0...v5.4.0).

Also see the changelog of the previous version, [v5.3.0](https://github.com/process-engine/bpmn-studio/releases/tag/v5.3.0).

## Major Features

- Live Execution Tracker Uses Events Instead Polling

## Features

- Started At Column on Process List (Dashboard)
- Make Process ID Editable
- Bugfixes
- Style Improvements

## Fixed Issues

- #1452 :lipstick: Bad UX when stoppig process
- #1480 :sparkles: Allow Editing the Process ID
- #1482 :recycle: Cannot save diagram when linter has errors
- #1488 :bug: Can not start processes if the previous opened diagram had linter errors

## Full Changelog

- b7861c96 :bug: Apply Fix for ParallelJoinGateway Resumption
- b309f79a :bug: Fix Bug Where Starting Processes is Not Possible
- 582fce09 :bug: Fix Resumption of FlowNodes With Multiple FlowNodeInstances
- a3fd8246 :sparkles: Add createdAt Column and Sort Correlation-List
- 738d322c :sparkles: Allow Saving Diagrams With Linter Errors
- b25f8430 :sparkles: Make Process ID Editable
- 1ee6e3cf :sparkles: Use Events for LET

# Release Notes BPMN-Studio v5.3.0

This changelog _only_ covers the changes between [v5.2.0 and v5.3.0](https://github.com/process-engine/bpmn-studio/compare/v5.2.0...v5.3.0).

Also see the changelog of the previous version, [v5.2.0](https://github.com/process-engine/bpmn-studio/releases/tag/v5.2.0).

## Major Features

- Disable Editing on Remote Solutions
- Navigate to Remote Diagram After Deploy

## Other Features

- Add Super Admin Claim
- Various bug fixes

## Fixed Issues

- #1461 :bug: Erroneous TimerStartEvent: ProcessInstance Is Not Stopable or Deletable
- #1467 :sparkles: Disable Possibility to Edit Remote Diagrams
- #1469 :sparkles: Navigate to Remote Solution After Deploy
- #1471 :bug: Request Overload on Inspect/Dashboard

## Full Changelog

- e43f236b :bug: Fix E2E Tests
- 81638663 :bug: Fix Handling of TimerStartEvents
- 498f842d :bug: Fix Wrong Usage of Credential Store
- bce55806 :bug: Fix Zoom When Opening Diagrams
- c21665c2 :recycle: Use setTimeout Instead of setInterval
- 8591d24f :sparkles: Add Super Admin Claim to Processengine-Runtime
- 1a78fbcc :sparkles: Disable Editing on Remote Solutions
- 8b654513 :sparkles: Navigate to Remote Diagram After Deploy

# Release Notes BPMN-Studio v5.2.0

This changelog _only_ covers the changes between [v5.1.2 and v5.2.0](https://github.com/process-engine/bpmn-studio/compare/v5.1.2...v5.2.0).

Also see the changelog of the previous version, [v5.1.2](https://github.com/process-engine/bpmn-studio/releases/tag/v5.1.2).

## Major Features

- Refactor Updating
- Add Default Sequence Flows Support

## Other Features

- Disable Timer Validation
- Disable Navigation After Deployment of a Diagram
- Remove Linux Build
- Various Bug Fixes

## Fixed Issues

- #1367 :sparkles: Add Progress bar When Downloading Updates
- #1439 :bug: Automatic Switch to Remote Solution after Deployment
- #1445 :bug: Copy and Paste Does Sometimes Break the Modeler

## Full Changelog

- 8fc03954 :bug: Disable Timer Validation
- 4d1866a1 :bug: Fix Copy of UserTasks When no Fields are Specified
- fec2fec0 :fire: Remove Linux Build
- 4066ce05 :recycle: :lipstick: Fix Naming Inconsistencies
- 86e47f6d :recycle: Dont Navigate on Deployment of a Diagram
- c165710b :recycle: Improve Changelog Creation
- 0f78f469 :recycle: Refactor Updating
- c882e525 :sparkles: Add Default Sequence Flows Support
- 0fd7c9c8 :wrench: Improve E2E Test Log
